{
  "texts": [
    "Ultra-high molecular weight (UHMW) DNA was isolated from frozen human brain tissues using a Bionano Prep SP Tissue and Tumor DNA Isolation kit (no.",
    "80038) according to the Bionano Prep SP Brain Tissue Isolation Tech Note (no. 3400).",
    "In short, approximately 20 mg of frozen tissue was homogenized using a Qiagen TissueRuptor (no.",
    "9002755), passed through a 40-µm filter and treated sequentially with Qiagen protease (cat. no.",
    "19155), proteinase K and RNAse A in lysis and binding buffer."
  ]
}